    "Hi-Drive, focusing on integrating automated vehicles in mixed traffic, Fig. 3 Representational similarity analysis of confusions between isolated body parts and full body from [98] emphasizes understanding user interactions with AVs, employing a multi-disciplinary approach with diverse studies to analyze user behavior, expectations, and limitations.",
